										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Today, I&#8217;m sharing the delightfully whimsical work of Mark Page.  Click any image to find out how to purchase a print!<br />
<a href="http://fineartamerica.com/profiles/mark-page.html?tab=artworkgalleries&amp;artworkgalleryid=344929" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/27e53-steamrhino_web.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="390" /></a><a href="http://fineartamerica.com/profiles/mark-page.html?tab=artworkgalleries&amp;artworkgalleryid=344929" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/32c59-page_zeppelinairship.jpg" alt="" width="273" height="195" /></a><a href="http://fineartamerica.com/profiles/mark-page.html?tab=artworkgalleries&amp;artworkgalleryid=344929" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/ef37d-page_maroonfishflyer.jpg" alt="" width="273" height="195" /></a><a href="http://fineartamerica.com/profiles/mark-page.html?tab=artworkgalleries&amp;artworkgalleryid=344929" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/dd19b-steamgorilla_web.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="390" /></a><a href="http://fineartamerica.com/profiles/mark-page.html?tab=artworkgalleries&amp;artworkgalleryid=344929" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="http://images.fineartamerica.com/images-medium-large-5/the-blue-legion-mark-page.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="390" /></a><a href="http://fineartamerica.com/profiles/mark-page.html?tab=artworkgalleries&amp;artworkgalleryid=344929" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/d6368-steamorgangrinder_web.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="390" /></a><br />
Aren&#8217;t these lovely?  Check out<a href="http://mpageworkshop.blogspot.com/" target="_blank"> Mark Page&#8217;s blog</a> for more info on his work.</p>
<p style="color:#36312d;">—</p>
<p style="color:#36312d;">Are you an artist/photographer/sculptor who loves Steampunk as much as I do?   Would you like to see your work featured on this blog?  Or, do you know of someone else who’s work you adore?  Please leave a comment on this post with a link or two!   I’ll happily feature anything that I think will fit the style of my blog.  And even if I don’t feature it, please please leave your info in a comment anyway!  More art is always better than less.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
